milestones.description: Pakistan's 165 is the lowest score in ODIs. They broke the earlier record of 179
Mark Burgess and Ken Wadsworth's 45-run partnership is the highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 26 between Rod Marsh and Greg Chappell
Saleem Altaf and Wasim Bari's 33-run partnership is the highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Alan Knott and Bob Woolmer
